WEBVTT

00:00:00.110 --> 00:00:02.820
Desiderio gives TYPO3 fourteen point three

00:00:03.050 --> 00:00:06.000
a complete editorial design system.

00:00:06.110 --> 00:00:08.660
Its two hundred forty-four content elements come from

00:00:08.660 --> 00:00:11.320
forty-nine typed Fluid components, with

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:14.800
backend previews and Visual Editor support.

00:00:14.910 --> 00:00:17.390
Fifteen runtime presets restyle a site

00:00:17.420 --> 00:00:19.800
or page subtree without rebuilding.

00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:21.890
Innesto then turns compatible shadcn

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:24.500
registry components into new Content Blocks.
